<!--
  Adapted from android_device_samsung_j1xlte's power_profile.xml.

  battery.capacity corrected to 2200 (mAh) - confirmed via multiple
  independent spec sources (GSMArena, Icecat, GSMChoice, TechBuz) for the
  real SM-G389F, which differs from the J1 2016's 2050mAh.

  Everything else (screen/radio/wifi/cpu power draw estimates, cpu.speeds
  table) is inherited from j1xlte unverified. The cpu.speeds table should
  be accurate regardless since both devices share the exact same exynos3475
  SoC (confirmed extensively elsewhere in this project), but the per-
  component mAh draw estimates would need real on-device measurement to
  verify precisely - inheriting reasonable estimates from a same-chipset
  device is standard/acceptable practice here, not something to block on.
-->
